# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DEMO SPECIFIC
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Synthetic data (keep generators, ignore output)
synthetic_data_output/
generated_clients.json

# Demo screenshots/videos (too large for repo)
demo_assets/*.mp4
demo_assets/*.mov
demo_assets/screenshots/*.png

# Pitch deck exports (keep source .pptx)
pitch_deck/*.pdf

# =============================================================================
# ALLOWED FILES (Explicitly NOT ignored)
# =============================================================================
# Config templates
!.env.example
!secrets.example.txt

# Knowledge Base templates
!knowledge_base/servicios/_TEMPLATE.md
!knowledge_base/faqs/_TEMPLATE.md
!knowledge_base/protocolos/_TEMPLATE.md

# Documentation
!README.md
!CHANGELOG*.md
!TODO*.md
!RESUMEN*.md

# =============================================================================
# NOTAS
# =============================================================================
# 1. Nunca commitear .env con API keys reales
# 2. Usar .env.example para documentar estructura
# 3. Bases de datos locales son temporales (demo)
# 4. Knowledge Base .md files SÍ se commitean (son contenido)
# =============================================================================
